# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# MyFinPro — Staging Environment Variable Schema
# This template shows ALL required variables for the staging environment.
# Values are injected from GitHub Secrets at deploy time — no persistent .env on the server.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── MySQL Database ──
# MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD  — Root password for MySQL (from GitHub Secrets)
# MYSQL_DATABASE       — Database name (e.g., myfinpro_staging)
# MYSQL_USER           — Database user (e.g., myfinpro_staging)
# MYSQL_PASSWORD       — Database user password (from GitHub Secrets)

# ── Database Connection ──
# DATABASE_URL         — Full connection string: mysql://USER:PASS@mysql:3306/DB_NAME

# ── Authentication ──
# JWT_SECRET           — Secret for signing JWT access tokens (min 32 chars)
# JWT_REFRESH_SECRET   — Secret for signing JWT refresh tokens (min 32 chars)

# ── Redis ──
# REDIS_URL            — Redis connection string (e.g., redis://redis:6379)

# ── Application Config ──
# NODE_ENV             — Environment: staging
# API_PORT             — API server port: 3001
# CORS_ORIGIN          — Allowed CORS origins: * (staging allows all)
# LOG_LEVEL            — Logging level: debug
# SWAGGER_ENABLED      — Enable Swagger docs: true
# RATE_LIMIT_TTL       — Rate limit window in ms: 60000
# RATE_LIMIT_MAX       — Max requests per window: 60

# ── Frontend Config ──
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL  — Public API URL for browser requests: /api
# API_INTERNAL_URL     — Internal API URL for SSR: http://api:3001

# ── Docker Image Config ──
# GHCR_REPO            — GitHub Container Registry repo (lowercase): owner/myfinpro
# IMAGE_TAG            — Docker image tag: staging
